---
import GithubIcon from "./icons/GithubIcon.astro";
---
<article class="flex flex-col px-2 gap-8">
  <section class="flex  justify-center items-center flex-wrap gap-8">
    <div class="shadow-lg">
      <img
        src="/icon.jpg"
        class="rounded-3xl h-80 w-56 hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-500 border-2 border-blue-400"
        alt=""
      />
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col max-w-xl gap-8">
      <div class="rounded-3xl hover:scale-105 p-4 border-2 border-blue-400 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-gray-200 hover:to-gray-300 dark:to-gray-900 dark:hover:to-gray-800 hover:transition-transform hover:duration-1000 shadow-lg">
        Mi nombre es <strong> Deyverson Herrera,</strong> empecé en el mundo de la
        programación/desarrollo en 2022, actualmente estudiante <strong
          >de Mecatrónica y Desarrollo Web.</strong>
      </div>
      <section class="flex w-full gap-8">
        <div class="w-4/12 cursor-pointer bg-gradient-to-b hover:scale-105 from-transparent via-transparent to-gray-200 hover:to-gray-300 dark:to-gray-900 dark:hover:to-gray-800 hover:transition-transform hover:duration-1000 border-2 rounded-3xl p-3 border-blue-400 items-center justify-center flex flex-col shadow-lg">
          <img src="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/126831007?v=4" class="w-14 rounded-full h-14" alt="" />
          <div class="flex flex-col text-black dark:text-white justify-center items-center pt-2">
            <h2 class="dark:text-gray-400 text-gray-800">@Deyverson1</h2>
          <GithubIcon class="size-6"/>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full bg-gradient-to-b text-black dark:text-white from-transparent to-gray-200 dark:to-gray-900 dark:hover:to-gray-800 hover:to-gray-300 hover:transition-transform hover:duration-1000 flex justify-around hover:scale-105  gap-4 rounded-3xl border-2 border-blue-400 h-full p-4 shadow-lg">
          <section>
            Hobbies:
          <div>
            <h1>Música</h1>
            <h1>Anime</h1>
            <h1>Futbol</h1>
            <h1>Videojuegos</h1>
          </div>
          </section>
          <section>
            Projects:
            <div>
              <h1>Replica Dropi.co</h1>
              <h1>Replica Bancolombia</h1>
              <h1>Búsqueda de Anime</h1>
              <h1>Búsqueda de Libros</h1>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    <section class="rounded-3xl hover:scale-105 md:mx-7 p-4 border-2 border-blue-400 dark:border-blue-400 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-gray-200 hover:to-gray-300 dark:to-gray-900 dark:hover:to-gray-800 dark:only:hover:to-gray-800  hover:transition-transform hover:duration-1000 shadow-lg">
      Mi enfoque principal se encuentra en la creación de experiencia de usuario
      atractivas y eficientes, por lo que como programador me he dedicado a
      adquirir diversos conocimientos que me ayuden en el enfoque de diferentes
      proyectos, desde <strong>ReactJs </strong> hasta <strong>MySQL</strong>
    </section>
  </section>
</article>


<style>
  strong {
    color: #4299e1;
  }
  h1{
    color: #a0aec0;
  }
</style>
